features: Practical V Shape Nozzle Design: this laundry liquid dispenser features a practical V shape nozzle design made from quality glass; This practical design ensures a smooth, non drip operation, providing a clean and simple laundry experience with daily use, the natural color of the glass makes this dispenser blend into your room decoration, creating a neat and orderly surrounding

Quantity to Help Your Operation: your package comes with 3 glass laundry detergent dispensers, an ample amount to accommodate your laundry needs; With the included 6 labels (designed on a piece of paper), and a counting cup (about 100 ml in capacity), you can accurately measure your laundry liquid each wash, optimizing usage and allowing you to keep track of your laundry supplies efficiently

Reliable Workmanship for Lasting Service: the reliable workmanship of these fabric softener dispensers is evident in the sturdy glass construction of the bottles; Built for longevity, they will resist wear and tear associated with frequent use and refills, the handle is easy to grip, and the label is waterproof, offering you lasting service while maintaining their sophisticated aesthetic appeal

Proper Dimension to Apply: sized at approximately 3.54 x 10.24 inches/ 9 x 26 cm, these detergent dispensers offer an ideal balance between capacity and counter space utilization; The bottles can hold up to about 50 oz/ 1500 ml of liquid, sufficient for numerous wash cycles, and the labels are sized at about 3.54 x 3.35 inches/ 9 x 8.5 cm, large enough to easily identify your laundry liquids

Practical Gifts for Others: this laundry detergent dispenser is a practical gift ideal for family members, relatives, homeowners, or someone looking to organize their laundry supplies; Not only will they receive stylish and convenient store solutions with these solid glass dispensers, but they will also appreciate the additional labels and counting cups for easier and organized operation
body.description: Features: Suitable for various occasions and settings, these laundry detergent dispensers are adaptable. Be them busy commercial stores or small household laundry rooms. Their lasting clear appeal, practical V shape nozzle design, and adequate fill capacity ensure they serve well in varying circumstances. Despite the glass construction, these laundry soap dispensers are lightweight and easy to carry. You can effortlessly refill them with your chosen laundry liquid, carry them around as needed, and store them safely when not in use. Comfort, ease of use, and efficiency are beautifully wrapped up in each one of these dispensers. Specifications: Bottle material: glass Bottle color: clear Size: Dispenser: about 3.54 x 10.24 inches/ 9 x 26 cm Capacity: about 50 oz/ 1500 ml Label: about 3.54 x 3.35 inches/ 9 x 8.5 cm Counting cup: about 100 ml in capacity Package includes: 3 x Laundry liquid dispensers 6 x Labels 1 x Counting cup Notes: Manual measurement, please allow slight errors on size.
